{"data": [{"id": "4741432", "title": "Omega Healthcare: Back To Pre-Pandemic Levels, But I Think It Consolidates (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It\u2019s been a satisfying year for Omega Healthcare Investors (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OHI\" title=\"Omega Healthcare Investors, Inc.\">OHI</a></span>) investors as shares have appreciated by over 30%, causing them to settle above $40 and reach their pre-pandemic levels. I remained bullish on OHI during the pandemic while shares hovered around the $30</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741432-omega-healthcare-back-to-pre-pandemic-levels-but-i-think-it-consolidates-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 02:00:00"}, {"id": "4741601", "title": "SIGA Technologies Vs Emergent BioSolutions: Product Portfolio And Future Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female doctor prohibiting access to a restricted area\" data-id=\"1211986569\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"567px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">doble-d/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p><b>SIGA Technologies, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIGA\" title=\"SIGA Technologies, Inc.\">SIGA</a></span>) (\u201cSiga\u201d) is a pharmaceutical company focused on developing and commercializing therapeutics for the prevention or treatment of infectious diseases. Their lead product is <a href=\"https://www.siga.com/tpoxx\" rel=\"nofollow\">TPOXX</a> (Tecovirimat), an antiviral treatment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211986569/image_1211986569.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741601-siga-technologies-vs-emergent-biosolutions-product-portfolio-and-future-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:49:22"}, {"id": "4741599", "title": "KE Holdings: Upside Is Attractive, But I Prefer To Wait For More Proof", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view over houses in Paris suburb\" data-id=\"1500297506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment overview</h2> <p>I give a hold rating for KE Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BEKE\" title=\"KE Holdings Inc.\">BEKE</a></span>) as I await more proof that the current demand improvement trend is sustainable. Specifically, I would need to see growth acceleration, backed by improving demand at the macro</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741599-ke-holdings-stock-attractive-upside-but-prefer-to-await-more-proof", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:45:22"}, {"id": "4741598", "title": "FS KKR Capital: A 13% Yield And Repricing Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Yield Road Sign Post Over a Blue Sky\" data-id=\"155095389\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5600px\" height=\"3743px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ryasick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>FS KKR Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FSK\" title=\"FS KKR Capital Corp\">FSK</a></span>) has seen a consistent narrowing of the gap between share price and net asset value in the second half of 2024 which is a result of the BDC improving its balance sheet quality</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155095389/image_155095389.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741598-fs-kkr-capital-a-13-percent-yield-and-repricing-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:38:37"}, {"id": "4741596", "title": "Global-E Online Ltd.: Positive Demand Environment Should Enable Growth Acceleration", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman purchasing clothes on a mobile app\" data-id=\"1744124538\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Alistair Berg</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>I am positive about Global-E Online Ltd. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLBE\" title=\"Global-E Online Ltd.\">GLBE</a></span>). My summarized thesis is that the demand environment has seemingly improved for GLBE, and that the new products/enhancements rolled out should enable GLBE to capitalize on this improving</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1744124538/image_1744124538.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741596-global-e-online-positive-demand-environment-should-enable-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:18:47"}, {"id": "4741594", "title": "Volkswagen: Halfway To Becoming Kodak 2.0", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Student Activist Leading Protest with Megaphone\" data-id=\"1705606794\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Giuseppe Lombardo/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>The analogy with Kodak</h2> <p>By the 1970s Kodak controlled 95% of the film market and 85% of the camera market; its dominance was blatant and no one else could hold a candle to it. Everything changed when Fujifilm, a Japanese company that offered film and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1705606794/image_1705606794.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741594-volkswagen-halfway-to-becoming-kodak-2-0", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 01:06:41"}, {"id": "4741593", "title": "Delek US Holdings: Dividends Are Safe For Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dollar in a box\" data-id=\"1211849923\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1211849923/image_1211849923.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Background</strong></h2> <p>The small independent refiner, Delek US Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DK\" title=\"Delek US Holdings, Inc.\">DK</a></span>), hereon referred to as \u201cDelek\u201d or \u201cthe parent company\u201d, endured a wild ride across th